#bold[#magenta[Synopsis:]] steroids module #bold[command] #cyan[--options]

  Run actions related to custom module development

#bold[#magenta[Available commands:]]

  module create #bold[directory]

    Create a new Module Development Harness in the target directory.

#bold[#magenta[Available commands in a Module Development Harness directory:]]

  module init #cyan[--options]

    Connect the development environment to an AppGyver Enterprise application.

    Find out more at: https://composer2.appgyver.com/modules/connect

  module refresh

    Refresh local information about the connected AppGyver Enterprise
    application.

  module deploy

    Package a custom module and deploy it to the AppGyver Cloud.

  module install <name>

    Install an external Composer Module in your development environment to be
    able to link to it through Supersonic.

    Find installable Modules at: https://composer2.appgyver.com/web_components
